WEBVTT

00:00:00.735 --> 00:00:03.024
How many of you are creatives,

00:00:03.048 --> 00:00:06.672
designers, engineers,
entrepreneurs, artists,

00:00:06.696 --> 00:00:09.083
or maybe you just have
a really big imagination?

00:00:09.107 --> 00:00:10.955
Show of hands? (Cheers)

00:00:10.979 --> 00:00:12.160
That's most of you.

00:00:13.334 --> 00:00:15.628
I have some news for us creatives.

00:00:16.714 --> 00:00:19.287
Over the course of the next 20 years,

00:00:21.471 --> 00:00:24.444
more will change around
the way we do our work

00:00:25.382 --> 00:00:27.539
than has happened in the last 2,000.

00:00:28.511 --> 00:00:33.139
In fact, I think we're at the dawn
of a new age in human history.